---
---

<section id="servizi" class="py-20 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-5">
    <div
      class="fade flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-end justify-between gap-4 mb-12"
    >
      <div>
        <div
          class="inline-block bg-orange-light text-orange text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full mb-4"
        >
          Cosa facciamo
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-navy leading-tight">
          I nostri servizi
        </h2>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div
      class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-px bg-gray-200 rounded-3xl overflow-hidden border border-gray-200 fade d1 shadow-2xl shadow-navy/5"
    >
      <!-- Analisi -->
      <div
        class="bg-white p-10 group hover:bg-cream transition-all duration-500 relative"
      >
        <div
          class="w-12 h-12 bg-cream-dark rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-8 border border-black/5"
        >
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            class="w-6 h-6 fill-navy/60"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            ><path
              d="M19 3H5c-1.1 0-2 .9-2 2v14c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h14c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V5c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zm-2 10h-4v4h-2v-4H7v-2h4V7h2v4h4v2z"
            ></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-black text-navy text-xl mb-4 tracking-tight">
          Analisi Trasparente
        </h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed font-light">
          Leggiamo la tua bolletta insieme a te. Ti spieghiamo ogni singola voce
          e identifichiamo insieme i costi inutili che puoi eliminare oggi
          stesso.
        </p>
        <a
          href="#contatti"
          class="mt-8 flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-orange opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-all"
        >
          Inizia da qui →
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Cambio -->
      <div
        class="bg-white p-10 group hover:bg-cream transition-all duration-500 relative"
      >
        <div
          class="w-12 h-12 bg-orange-light rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-8 border border-orange/10"
        >
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            class="w-6 h-6 fill-orange"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            ><path
              d="M16 17V14H9V10H16V7L21 12L16 17ZM2 12L7 7V10H14V14H7V17L2 12Z"
            ></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-black text-navy text-xl mb-4 tracking-tight">
          Scelta Consapevole
        </h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed font-light">
          Ti accompagniamo nella scelta del fornitore ideale. Ci occupiamo di
          ogni pratica burocratica, assicurandoci che tutto avvenga con la
          massima correttezza.
        </p>
        <a
          href="#contatti"
          class="mt-8 flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-orange opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-all"
        >
          Scopri di più →
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Business -->
      <div
        class="bg-white p-10 group hover:bg-cream transition-all duration-500 relative"
      >
        <div
          class="w-12 h-12 bg-navy-light/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-8 border border-navy-light/10"
        >
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            class="w-6 h-6 fill-navy-light"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            ><path
              d="M12 7V3H2v18h20V7H12zM6 19H4v-2h2v2zm0-4H4v-2h2v2zm0-4H4V9h2v2zm0-4H4V5h2v2zm10 12h-2v-2h2v2zm0-4h-2v-2h2v2zm0-4h-2V9h2v2zm0-4h-2V5h2v2zm4 12h-2v-2h2v2zm0-4h-2v-2h2v2z"
            ></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-black text-navy text-xl mb-4 tracking-tight">
          Supporto Aziendale
        </h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed font-light">
          Per negozi e PMI offriamo una consulenza strategica. Ottimizziamo i
          costi energetici per proteggere i profitti della tua attività locale.
        </p>
        <a
          href="#contatti"
          class="mt-8 flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-orange opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-all"
        >
          Piani Business →
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Assistenza -->
      <div
        class="bg-white p-10 group hover:bg-cream transition-all duration-500 relative"
      >
        <div
          class="w-12 h-12 bg-navy/5 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-8 border border-navy/5"
        >
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            class="w-6 h-6 fill-navy/60"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            ><path
              d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm1 15h-2v-6h2v6zm0-8h-2V7h2v2z"
            ></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-black text-navy text-xl mb-4 tracking-tight">
          Referenti Dedicati
        </h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed font-light">
          Il nostro rapporto non finisce con una firma. Restiamo il tuo punto di
          riferimento per ogni dubbio, variazione o assistenza post-vendita.
        </p>
        <a
          href="#contatti"
          class="mt-8 flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-orange opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-all"
        >
          Sempre al tuo fianco →
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Mercato -->
      <div
        class="bg-white p-10 group hover:bg-cream transition-all duration-500 relative border-l border-gray-100"
      >
        <div
          class="w-12 h-12 bg-orange-light/30 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-8 border border-orange/5"
        >
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            class="w-6 h-6 fill-orange"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            ><path
              d="M11 15h2v2h-2zm0-8h2v6h-2zm.99-5C6.47 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.47 10 9.99 10C17.52 22 22 17.52 22 12S17.52 2 11.99 2zM12 20c-4.42 0-8-3.58-8-8s3.58-8 8-8 8 3.58 8 8-3.58 8-8 8z"
            ></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-black text-navy text-xl mb-4 tracking-tight">
          Guida al Mercato
        </h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed font-light">
          Ti aiutiamo a navigare nella fine del mercato tutelato. Ti spieghiamo
          esattamente cosa sta succedendo per non farti trovare impreparato.
        </p>
        <a
          href="#contatti"
          class="mt-8 flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-orange opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-all"
        >
          Leggi i dettagli →
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Rinnovabile -->
      <div
        class="bg-white p-10 group hover:bg-cream transition-all duration-500 relative"
      >
        <div
          class="w-12 h-12 bg-green-light border border-green/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-8"
        >
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            class="w-6 h-6 fill-green"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            ><path
              d="M17 8C8 10 5.9 16.17 3.82 21.34L5.71 22L6.66 19.7C7.14 19.87 7.64 20 8.15 20C11.3 20 14.04 18.22 15.43 15.59L17.27 15.89L18 14.11L16.2 13.81C16.92 12.01 17 10.05 17 8zM9.5 12C9.5 14.48 11.52 16.5 14 16.5C14.16 16.5 14.32 16.49 14.47 16.47C13.29 17.41 11.79 18 10.15 18C7.5 18 5.48 16.32 4.97 14.05C6.18 13.06 7.73 12.33 9.4 12.04C9.44 12.03 9.47 12 9.5 12zM21 2L2 14L11 2L21 2z"
            ></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-black text-navy text-xl mb-4 tracking-tight">
          Scelta Sostenibile
        </h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed font-light">
          Crediamo nel valore dell'energia green. Ti mostriamo le migliori
          opzioni da fonti rinnovabili per unire etica, convenienza fiscale e
          stima per il futuro.
        </p>
        <a
          href="#contatti"
          class="mt-8 flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-orange opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-all"
        >
          Vai al Green →
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
